{"tid":257042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！港珠澳大橋工傷 工人高處墮下重傷","createTime":"2017-05-25T02:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-25T10:02:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"696ae193103e989ed0e3ab0f990bea9df5ba5127","tid":257042,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170525/large/1495680186_4150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170525%2Flarge%2F1495680186_4150.jpg&h=43aab02d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意外後工人即時收工。(讀者陳先生提供)(讀者提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋又發生工業意外。早上9時28分，香港口岸人工島上旅檢大樓的天幕部份，有工人由高處墮下。蘋民陳先生稱，他今早開工期間，上級突然叫停，向在場工人說：「人工島有個科文高處墮下，唔駛返工喇！」各人即時打卡收工。他對事件表示震驚，「以後會小心啲。」警方稱，人工島B1區，一名30多歲男子由高處墮下受傷，送往瑪嘉烈醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56739483&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56739483%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170525&d=1hWmPSacJKZtYHxjwETg5Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b6a91ddb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56739483%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170525&h=1b8b11b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56739483&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170525</a>"},{"pid":"126bc37304d25c408c4568ae8a2f9e1876d1bb87","tid":257042,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bab93b90b838bbbece5e1c0751b783ca26ddd3","tid":257042,