ockquote><br />\nExactly<br />\n不過港珠澳叫好d，頭盔安全鞋都戴足<br />\n但其他咩安全裝置，諗下好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高空工作要警覺 記得綁好安全索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真邊有咁多人理安全 又要趕工又剩</blockquote><br />\n唉依個真，有時自己落site企十二級梯頂又無人幫手。安全帶又無地方扣，叫客/公司約平台，佢地睬你都有味。 錢多但真係血汗錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申弱電撚"},{"pid":"09856014c54d44e40aea710fd1669ae174846305","tid":257042,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:52:19.000Z","msg":"政府成撚人叫人安全<br />\n最唔安全就係政府自己<br />\n正一垃圾基建<br />\n死人工程<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7257bfe981fc58a9f46fe6a1f81a3b55d4f6db68","tid":257042,"uid":7905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:53:08.000Z","msg":"好想睇佢起好之後冧左佢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾千億造啲大白象 都唔比啲錢落民生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65e26553774df503d109a3e976feb10c0e70e06","tid":257042,"uid":111192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"希望個科文冇事"},{"pid":"4dc8397c873a483f5ccd309989943c43665a32da","tid":257042,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"應該破到西班牙聖家堂既建築時間紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55708eb2a3e5a0994071b151fd82fdd990e13784","tid":257042,"uid":69417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想睇佢起好之後冧左佢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾千億造啲大白象 都唔比啲錢落民生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.g