啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36139f562b26fd87e787352e4939affb1fcc3a2a","tid":257042,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:37:07.000Z","msg":"極危險"},{"pid":"36ae506d41e17ab9fe1abb801f5b54e775bb490d","tid":257042,"uid":63618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"呢啲只係因為死左人無得唔報，平時啲斷手斷腳野/高處墮下（唔死）一定多十倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做呢行既個個都知安全主任都係得個擺字，佢講明幾點會巡，啲科文判頭咪嗰個鐘數做場戲比佢睇，危險到戲都做唔到既咪唔做野住等佢行完先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d1aa6955fda6bbaa544f53c95d01ec77b7247d","tid":257042,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:50:15.000Z","msg":"又超資、又貪污、又回唔到本、又死得人多<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母香港啲錢俾啲垃圾高官敗撚晒"},{"pid":"7542b64f2e723b7ab6d5239e81bd8d9df47eb464","tid":257042,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又超資、又貪污、又回唔到本、又死得人多<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母香港啲錢俾啲垃圾高官敗撚晒</blockquote><br />\n家下深圳自己起多條同香港搶客, 由頭到尾用港珠澳做實習, 佢自己先起條堅既出黎, 香港俾錢人地學野炸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1916cd3c134bceda157e34c2cf8af71f6e63d654","tid":257042,"uid":16056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:04:08.000Z","msg":"日日係而條橋返工，聽啲師傅講而條橋啲安全算做得好足，但真係好撚邪每個月都死幾個咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5ac228e3984bd8d287e7c7e756ae80fb3ee65","tid":257042,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想睇佢起好之後冧左佢仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾千億造啲大白象 都唔比啲錢落民生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾千億倒落海就濕濕碎<br />\n一兩億用黎安老扶貧就好肉赤"},{"pid":"f61a6cfcf173bf3c7e4a2ae69391c878f567b348","tid":257042,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>把我們的血肉 築成我們新的長城<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n起來，不願做奴隸工人<br />\n把我們的血肉築成我們新的大橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港民族到了，最危險的時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起來，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">起來</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">起來</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273030ec50ca24e579ea403f28125d8824dc2702","tid":257042,"uid":52516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係冇咩安全野可以搞？<br />\n咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行過轉地盤就知其實真係冇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係安全官面前大家戲子<br />\n轉個頭就個個特技人</blockquote><br />\nExactly<br />\n不過港珠澳叫好d，頭盔安全鞋都戴足<br />\n但其他咩安全裝置，諗下好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高空工作要警覺 記得綁好安全索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真邊有咁多人理安全 又要趕工又剩</blockquote><br />\n唉依個真，有時自己落site企十二級梯頂又無人幫手。安全帶又無地方扣，叫客/公司約平台，佢地睬你都有味。 錢多但真係血汗錢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申弱電撚</blockquote><br />\n好多野出過事先知真係要小心<br />\n利申十二梯頂冼線跌落黎死唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcf4ce75f4725097ebf2e2f0ebb278f26ebfad5","tid":257042,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"又一件<br />\n打死我都唔用呢條血肉長城"},{"pid":"f4b36c190f7fab47240dad24518c41c6948d663f","tid":257042,"uid":25598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"奈何橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6aa410fa8874b25c1ca5b57c94a1beeb181be6","tid":257042,"uid":47823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真，工程要唔死人，除非擺多三倍金錢和時間，到時又話造價貴</blockquote><br />\n本身已經十倍金錢喇"},{"pid":"659e15e507fbb54b9636843ce7d5c133988fa197","tid":257042,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T06:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 夠喇，人命黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好再派人入去啦，由佢擺係到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}